name: Ticket: SI Birthday Party -  May13th
description:
We're having our 2nd birthday and celebrating with a party at the Tooting Tram and Social on Monday May 13th

Death At Sea will be headlining the evening with support from Yearbook and Luke Godwin. 

At just £3 a ticket (it will be £5 on the door), can you really say no?
